metadata.name: I N F I N I T E
metadata.description:
The particular version of my artwork "I N F I N I T E".
"Princess Aerin"
Aerin is an elven Princess that comes from the Ithilien kingdom. It is a fancy form of the name Erin, and has the meaning of being ‘O C E A N’.
-1/1 .

Created by Gerami on February 20, 2022.

The collector will get the original file in 7972x11500 pixels.
